text:
Rob Shuter reports…. Giuliana Rancic had just one demand for returning to E! — ditch Maria Menounos!

“When Giuliana left E!, she recommended Maria to replace her,” a source told The National ENQUIRER.

“She thought it would be the perfect fit.

Guiliana Rancic Looking Sicker Than Ever!

“But as soon as she left the building, Maria turned on Giuliana,” the source said, “making it impossible for both ladies to work together!”

“Now Maria is out of the picture — and Giuliana can’t wait to return!”
title: Giuliana Rancic’s E! Network Power Play
